I read thousands of messages people left just on March 26, the 49th day â€” the seventh day of the seventh week â€” since Dr. Liâ€™s death. Many Chinese believe that is the day that a personâ€™s soul will finally leave the body and be reincarnated as a newborn.

March 26 is also when Wuhan began to allow its residents to take back the ashes of their loved ones. People queued in long lines at funeral homes. The photos triggered social media discussions of the real scope of the outbreak and the credibility of governmentâ€™s official toll of Wuhanâ€™s dead. Many of the photos were subsequently censored.

